ta = that
wa = what
to = all prepositions

mu, mi = I/me, my
yu, yi = you, your
itu, iti = ri, ria
malu, mali = we, our
italu, itali = they, their

a: active
e: pasive
u: noun
i: adjective/adverb
o: preposition

bazita sur la skriba formo, mi forigas literojn
vorto ne finiĝu per konsonanto

yeso: jes (affirmative)
no: ne
(? maybe change to yesi, ni)
nu: mal

pi: past
wi: future
nowi: nun

? Remove r in roots if followed by a consonent ?

